					          <p id="d2117e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            If a retroactive downward price reduction occurs under a redeterminable contract that provides for progress payments, the contracting officer shall-</p>
