						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2117e27" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Determine the refund due and obtain repayment from the contractor for the excess of payments made for delivered items over amounts due as recomputed at the reduced prices; and</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2117e36" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Increase the unliquidated progress payments amount for overdeductions made from the contractorâ€™s billings for items delivered.</p>
						            </li>
